name: DecentralGPT
description: DecentralGPT is a decentralized AI large language model inference network that supports multiple open source large language models.Its design goal is to build a universal artificial intelligence (AGI) that is secure, privacy-preserving, democratic, transparent, open source, andavailable to everyone.This network takes advantage of many advantages of decentralized technology. Include enhanced data security, privacy protection, and improved efficiency and reducedcoststhrough distributed computing resources.
